&lt;p&gt;As a Sr Staff Engineer, you will co-own the technical vision for our storage services. This is a role with high autonomy, high visibility, and deep technical impact. You will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help define and lead the execution of a multi-year technical roadmap for Storage, pushing the boundaries of industry-leading query speeds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design tiered storage strategies (Hot/Warm/Cold), TTL-based data eviction, and optimization strategies that handle massive, real-time data influx.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with product, support, and other engineering teams to drive platform-wide storage standards, while leveling up the engineers around you.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thrive in our remote-first, highly collaborative culture where independence and clear communication are celebrated&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
